name: Structural Design
description: The Structural Design package supports various structural workflows in Dynamo and Revit. Take a look at the "extra" folder for some examples that can be used with the Dynamo Player. The version 2022.12 is compatible with Revit 2023.1 and Dynamo 2.16. A list of new nodes can be found in the structural-design-whats-new.txt file. Contact with the author if any questions: https://twitter.com/tomekf
